  "texts": [
    "This research should aim to develop adaptive robots that cater to the emotional and physical needs of dementia patients, enhancing their quality of life with a blend of cognitive support and companionship.",
    "In conclusion, the use of Large Language Models in dementia care represents a promising frontier in the intersection of AI and healthcare.",
    "While challenges and limitations exist, the potential benefits of LLMs in enhancing cognitive abilities, enriching social interaction, and supporting caregivers are undeniable.",
    "As we move forward, it is crucial that the development and implementation of LLMs is guided by ethical considerations, empirical evidence, and a commitment to improving the lives of individuals living with dementia.",
